    "en": {
      "title": "CBK to open Nawa Lanka Freedom Party Office",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The party office of the Nawa Lnka Freedom Party, led by MP Kumara Welgama, is due to be opened on Monday (5).",
        "The new party office will be opened by former President Chandrika Bandaranaike Kumaratunga.",
        "Parliamentarian Welgama said that the new party office will be established in Battaramulla, and said that youth below the age of 40 will be trained, and will be made into a corruption-free, youth political movement in the future."
      ],
